meanings.definition: (Leon) Bix Beiderbecke (1903-1931), an American jazz cornetist, pianist and composer.
meanings.english_definition: An American jazz cornetist, pianist and composer.

examples.sentence: Bix Beiderbecke was one of the most influential jazz musicians of the 1920s.
examples.translation: ビックス・バイダーベックは1920年代で最も影響力のあるジャズミュージシャンの一人でした。

etymology.value: The name is of German origin.
